Ylva the Cleaver
Master Hero (6 AP Build)
High Concept
A boisterous and joyful werewolf warrior who treats life, combat, and even butchery as the greatest game in the world. She is a whirlwind of infectious enthusiasm and terrifying, master-level violence—a "manic pixie muscle mommy" who finds pure, unadulterated fun in the thrill of the hunt.
Appearance
A powerfully built Nord woman whose physique is a testament to a life lived at full intensity. Her most striking feature is her hair, naturally split down the middle into two distinct colors—one side a shock of blood-red, the other spun gold. An innate mark, a sign she was born under the gaze of the Hunter. She is rarely still, often shifting her weight, cracking her knuckles, or grinning with an infectious, slightly feral energy. Her movements are bold and confident, taking up space and drawing the eye.

